{"word":"σχίζα","slug":"σχίζα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σχίζα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σχίζω'><el>σχίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a piece of wood cleft off, a lath, splinter</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>scindula</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>cleft wood, fire-wood</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>an arrow</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}